.insider.com%2F6887cb3ff748d8c055f665ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222061%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBluesky%20CEO%20Jay%20Graber%20said%20critical%20thinking%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20necessary%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Fast%20Company%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbluesky-jay-graber-interview-open-source-channels-podcast-peter-kafka-2025-6%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBluesky%20CEO%20Jay%20Graber%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20developing%20critical-thinking%20skills%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20necessary%26quot%3B%20in%20today's%20job%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20human%20oversight%20is%20needed%20and%20that%20you%20shouldn't%20%26quot%3Bfully%20outsource%20your%20thinking%26quot%3B%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGraber%20also%20believes%20that%20developing%20a%20generalist%20skillset%20is%20key%20to%20thriving%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20may%20be%20transforming%20your%20job%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-economist-teaching-kids-4-skills-to-prepare-for-ai-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecritical%20thinking%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20Bluesky%20CEO%20Jay%20Graber.%20She%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20developing%20critical-thinking%20skills%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20necessary%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20able%20to%20automate%20a%20lot%20of%20critical-reasoning%20tasks%2C%20and%20if%20we%20fully%20outsource%20our%20own%20reasoning%2C%20it's%20actually%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20run%20in%20an%20automated%20fashion%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGraber%2C%20who%20previously%20founded%20a%20social%20network%20focused%20on%20events%20called%20Happening%20Inc.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20you're%20a%20student%2C%20maybe%20that%20means%20writing%20your%20essays%20by%20hand%2C%20Graber%20said.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20build%20%26quot%3Bthe%20muscle%20for%20critical%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20keep%20it%20growing%2C%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20fully%20outsource%20your%20thinking%2C%20or%20an%20essay%2C%20to%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraber%20said%20that%20Bluesky%20uses%20AI%20in%20areas%20like%20moderation%20and%20curation%C2%A0but%20never%20lets%20it%20operate%20autonomously.%20She%20said%20employees%20check%20and%20revise%20the%20output%20and%20use%20critical%20thinking%20to%20decide%20what%20actually%20gets%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20let%20it%20run%20autonomously%2C%20it%20doesn't%20have%20actual%20context%20or%20intelligence%2C%20or%20the%20many%20things%20that%20we%20need%20as%20humans%20to%20make%20good%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20Graber%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20it's%20producing%20stuff%20that%20sounds%20or%20looks%20right%20without%20actually%20being%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9ede1ba-dee6-4ffe-b6e6-7f2ee24ef448%5C%22%3ECultivating%20a%20range%20of%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGraber%20advises%20embracing%20a%20generalist%20mindset.%20With%20AI%20providing%20%26quot%3Bspecialist%20expertise%20packaged%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20real%20value%20lies%20in%20discerning%20what's%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20the%20good%20judgment%20of%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20use%20it%2C%20and%20then%20you%20have%20to%20have%20the%20flexibility%20to%20take%20that%20knowledge%20and%20do%20something%20useful%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Graber%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-skills-learn-ai-era-tech-executives-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20skills%20are%20important%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%2C%20Graber%20st