e%20than%20at%20any%20other%20point%20in%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Goldman%20Sachs'%20headquarters%20at%20200%20West%20Street%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678fff3d2fcded5e90741790%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20headquarters%20at%20200%20West%20Street%20in%20Lower%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b885a063-e2ec-4938-bbf3-09740fe319ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20day-to-day%20of%20a%20busy%20summer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interns%20on%20Roth's%20team%20help%20the%20sales%20and%20trading%20executives%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20news%20ahead%20of%20markets%20opening%20and%20synthesize%20what's%20in%20their%20flooded%20inboxes%20each%20morning.%20Interns%20also%20get%20to%20work%20on%20market%20research%20%E2%80%94%20analyzing%20what%20goes%20into%20a%20good%20trade%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20do%20pitches%20for%20us%2C%20so%20once%20a%20week%20they'll%20show%20what%20they've%20learned%20on%20the%20desk%20that%20week%20and%20pitch%20a%20trade%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we'll%20ask%20them%20questions%20so%20they%20can%20really%20illustrate%20their%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Roth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20on%20the%20equities%20trading%20team%2C%20Henry%20pitched%20stocks%20that%20he%20said%20weren't%20just%20theoretical%20exercises%20%E2%80%94%20but%20real%20ideas%20that%20business%20leaders%20could%20act%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20researching%20real%20things%20that%20the%20desk%20would%20consider%20important%20to%20look%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20exciting%20part%20of%20the%20day%20for%20Henry%20(and%20what%20he%20said%20he%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20time%20on)%20has%20been%20sitting%20