%20it%20to%20show%20up%20in%20all%20these%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20people%20who%20had%20access%20to%20the%20records%20seized%20by%20the%20FBI%20say%20they%20found%20nothing%20to%20indicate%20that%20Epstein%20had%20any%20role%20with%20US%20or%20foreign%20intelligence.%20There's%20no%20sign%20that%20evidence%20was%20removed%20because%20it%20contained%20classified%20or%20sensitive%20information%2C%20they%20said.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20intelligence%20ties%20in%20court%20records%20or%20during%20the%20five-week%20trial%20of%20Epstein's%20accomplice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-sentencing-tearful-victims-statements-hearing-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGhislaine%20Maxwell%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-sex-trafficking-trial-verdict-reached-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econvicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20of%20trafficking%20girls%20to%20Epstein%20for%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20supports%20the%20contention%20that%20there%20was%20either%20a%20honeypot%20blackmail%20scheme%20or%20any%20association%20with%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20people%20with%20access%20to%20the%20seized%20records%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20had%20Epstein%20been%20working%20as%20an%20intelligence%20asset%20in%20some%20fashion%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20trace%20of%20that%20in%20the%20seized%20records.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20working%20for%20the%20government%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20information%20to%20the%20government%20%E2%80%94%20that%20relationship%20is%20something%20that%20neither%20party%20necessarily%20wants%20to%20casually%20be%20discovered%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Adam%20Hickey%2C%20a%20former%20top%20official%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice's%20national%20security%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHickey%2C%20who%20oversaw%20counterintelligence%2C%20espionage%2C%20and%20foreign%20computer%20hacking%20cases%2C%20had%20no%20involvement%20with%20the%20Epstein%20and%20Maxwell%20prosecutions.%20But%20he%20and%20other%20national%20security%20law%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it's%20notable%20that%20neither%20Epstein%20nor%20Maxwell%20raised%20intelligence%20connections%20in%20their%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20would%20expect%20him%20to%20want%20to%20prove%20that%20what%20he%20was%20doing%20was%20because%20the%20government%20sent%20him%20out%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Hickey%20says.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20fodder%20for%20a%20defense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-files-records-trump-admin-keeping-secret-may-release-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20backpedaling%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20promise%20to%20release%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emore%20documents%20from%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20Epstein%20files%20has%20reignited%20long-standing%20suspicions%20that%20the%20government%20is%20hiding%20details%20of%20Epstein's%20crimes%20and%20protecting%20his%20many%20powerful%20and%20influential%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-fbi-pick-share-award-trump-media-group-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFBI%20Director%20Kash%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20deputy%2C%20Dan%20Bongino%2C%20pushed%20for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BEpstein%20files%26quot%3B%20before%20joining%20the%20administration%2C%20claiming%20the%20government%20was%20participating%20in%20a%20cover-up.%20The%20idea%20that%20Epstein%20had%20some%20kind%20of%20intelligence%20role%20has%20been%20promoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-bannon-filmed-jeffrey-epstein-trump-friendship-documentary-tapes-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D