ot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshots-fired-new-york-building-houses-blackstone-kpmg-nypd-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshooting%20at%20345%20Park%20Avenue%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20evening%20left%20four%20victims%2C%20including%20a%20New%20York%20Police%20Department%20officer%2C%20dead.%20The%20gunman%2C%2027-year-old%20Shane%20Tamura%2C%20was%20also%20found%20dead%20at%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Monday%20night%2C%20NYPD%20Commissioner%20Jessica%20Tisch%20gave%20a%20timeline%20of%20how%20the%20shooting%20unfolded%20at%20the%20office%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6d8c9d8-a58a-447b-a3b0-d4a274221a07%5C%22%3E6%3A28%20p.m.%3A%20911%20calls%20start%20coming%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETisch%20said%20911%20call%20centers%20began%20receiving%20calls%20about%20an%20active%20shooter%20inside%20345%20Park%20Avenue%20at%206%3A28%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20surveillance%20video%20showed%20Tamura%20disembarking%20from%20a%20double-parked%20BMW%20on%20Park%20Avenue%20between%2051st%20and%2052nd%20streets.%20Tamura%20was%20carrying%20an%20M4%20rifle%20in%20his%20right%20hand%20as%20he%20walked%20to%20the%20building's%20entrance%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20building's%20security%20camera%20footage%20shows%20the%20shooter%20enter%20the%20lobby%2C%20turn%20right%2C%20and%20immediately%20open%20fire%20on%20an%20NYPD%20officer.%20He%20then%20shoots%20a%20woman%20who%20took%20cover%20behind%20a%20pillar%20and%20proceeds%20through%20the%20lobby%2C%20spraying%20it%20with%20gunfire%2C%26quot%3B%20Tisch%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20said%20at%20the%20same%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20NYPD%20officer%20who%20died%20in%20the%20shooting%20was%20Didarul%20Islam%2C%2036.%20Islam%20served%20in%20the%20NYPD's%2047th%20Precinct%20and%20was%20an%20immigrant%20from%20Bangladesh.%20He%20leaves%20behind%20his%20pregnant%20wife%20and%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETisch%20said%20Tamura%20then%20proceeded%20to%20the%20building's%20elevator%20bank%2C%20where%20he%20shot%20a%20security%20guard%20who%20was%20taking%20cover%20behind%20the%20security%20desk.%20Another%20man%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20lobby%2C%20Tisch%20said%2C%20citing%20a%20statement%20given%20by%20the%20individual%20after%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjjO32%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Midtown%20building%20is%20located%20on%20the%20west%20side%20of%20Manhattan%2C%20blocks%20from%20Grand%20Central%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjjO32%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b27b37d-3b8b-45d6-8131-bd636574170b%5C%22%3EThe%20shooter%20opens%20fire%20in%20Rudin%20Management's%20office%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20shooter%20then%20calls%20the%20elevator%2C%20which%20opens%20in%20the%20lobby.%20A%20female%20exits%20the%20elevator%2C%20and%20he%20allows%20her%20to%20walk%20past%20him%20unharmed.%20He%20goes%20up%20to%20the%2033rd%20floor%2C%20which%20is%20Rudin%20Management%2C%20and%20begins%20to%20walk%20the%20floor%20firing%20rounds%2C%26quot%3B%20Tisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERudin%20Management%20is%20a%20real%20estate%20company%20that%20owns%20345%20Park%20Avenue.%20The%20building's%20tenants%20include%20Blackstone%2C%20KPMG%2C%20and%20the%20NFL%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20he%20traveled%2C%20one%20person%20was%20struck%20and%20killed%20on%20that%20floor.%20He%20then%20proceeds%20down%20a%20hallway%20and%20shoots%20himself%20in%20the%20chest%2C%26quot%3B%20Tisch%20said%20of%20Tamura's%20final%20moments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20victims%20%E2%80%94%20Islam%20and%20three%20civilians%20%E2%80%94%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20A%20fifth%20victim%20was%20in%20critical%20condition%20at%20press%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETisch%20said%20four%20other%20victims%20were%20receiving%20treatment%20for%20%26quot%3Bminor%20injuries%26quot%3B%20they%20had%20sustained%20while%20trying%20to%20flee%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b69bac6b-1b40-48f6-a156-3f3ccca30285%5C%22%3EShooter's%20double-parked%20BMW%20searched%2C%20firearm%20found%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETisch%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20double-parked%20BMW%20was%20registered%20to%20Tamura.%20When%20officers%20searched%20the%20vehicle%2C%20they%20found%20a%20rifle%20case%20with%20rounds%2C%20a%20loaded%20revolver%2C%20ammunition%2C%20magazines%2C%20a%20backpack%2C%20and%20medication%20prescribed%20to%20Tamura.%20The%20bomb%20squad%20said%20the%20vehicle%20was%20found%20to%20be%20clear%20of%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETamura%20had%20driven%20through%20Colorado%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Nebraska%20and%20Iowa%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%20then%20Columbia%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20%26quot%3Bas%20recently%20as%204%3A24%20p.m.%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%20before%20arriving%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20Tisch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20our%20law%20enforcement%20partners%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Mr.%20Tamura%20has%20a%20documented%20mental%20health%20history.%20His%20motives%20are%20still%20under%20investigation%2C%20and%20we%20are%20working%20to%20understand%20why%20he%20targeted%20this%20particular%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20Tisch%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Raia%2C%20the%20assistant%20director%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20FBI's%20New%20York%20field%20office%2C%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20FBI%20agents%20were%20immediately%20deployed%20to%20the%20scene.%20The%20shooting%20%26quot%3Bremains%20an%20NYPD%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Raia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitial%20checks%20of%20our%20internal%20systems