asool%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Aroma%20Mission%2C%20for%20example%2C%20encourages%20the%20cultivation%20of%20aromatic%20crops%20across%20different%20regions.%20This%20helps%20farmers%20build%20value%20chains%20that%20produce%20sustainable%20raw%20materials%2C%20which%20are%20then%20used%20indigenously%20to%20develop%20finished%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Aroma%20Mission%20has%20identified%20lavender%20as%20the%20most%20suitable%20crop%20due%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20cooler%20climate.%20Rasool%20shares%20that%20the%20mission%20has%20gained%20momentum%20since%20its%20launch%20in%202017.%20In%20the%20plains%2C%20crops%20like%20lemongrass%2C%20mint%2C%20and%20roses%20are%20promoted.%20But%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20lavender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20hilly%20areas%2C%20maize%20used%20to%20get%20destroyed%20by%20wild%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20lavender%2C%20with%20its%20strong%20scent%2C%20naturally%20repels%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20crop%20that%20fits%20both%20the%20land%20and%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20support%20has%20helped%20too.%20Farmers%20receive%20subsidies%20of%20%E2%82%B92000%20to%20%E2%82%B95000%20per%20kanal%20for%20planting%20material.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20set%20up%20our%20own%20distillation%20unit.%20That%20increased%20our%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20a%20local%20farmer%20from%20Pulwama.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20still%20need%20better%20marketing%20channels%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20Doda%20or%20Kishtwar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20experiment%20to%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20with%20lavender%20since%202015%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20say%20I%E2%80%99m%20emotionally%20connected%20to%20it%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ghulam%20Mohiudin%2C%20a%20farmer%20from%20Budgam.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20spent%20a