%2C%20he%20says%20he%20works%20every%20day%20and%20barely%20has%20time%20for%20a%20drink%20himself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELorenzo%20Antinori%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20founder%20of%20the%20world's%20second-best%20bar%2C%20hardly%20ever%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Italian%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efounded%20Bar%20Leone%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-trip-hong-kong-vacation-solo-travel-surprised-food-minibus-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHong%20Kong%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%20Just%20five%20years%20later%2C%20in%202024%2C%20The%20World's%2050%20Best%20Restaurants%20ranked%20it%20the%20second-best%20bar%20in%20the%20world%2C%20clinching%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20won%20the%20same%20award%20in%202025%2C%20edged%20out%20of%20the%20top%20spot%20worldwide%20by%20the%20Handshake%20Speakeasy%20in%20Mexico%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAntinori%20manages%20the%20bar%20seven%20days%20a%20week%20and%20is%20working%20on%20opening%20his%20second%20bar%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20this%20month.%20He's%20single%2C%20drinks%20a%20Negroni%20once%20to%20twice%20a%20month%2C%20and%2C%20after%20a%20career%20full%20of%20twists%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eregrets%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a132d1cf-95a3-41ef-aaf9-ad4697e79c83%5C%22%3ELaw%20school%2C%20banana%20farm%20worker%2C%20and%20finally%20bar%20owner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAntinori%20went%20to%20law%20school%20in%20Rome%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20says%20law%20felt%20%26quot%3Btoo%20stiff%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20after%20three%20years%20in%20law%20school%2C%20he%20dropped%20out%20and%20booked%20a%20one-way%20flight%20to%20Australia.%20There%2C%20he%20dabbled%20in%20everything%20from%20working%20on%20a%20banana%20farm%20to%20being%20a%20barback%20in%20a%20strip%20joint%20and%20a%20hostel%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20short%20bartending%20stints%20at%20The%20Savoy%20in%20London%20and%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Hotel%20in%20Seoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20had%20experience%20working%20in%20the%20nightlife.%20So%20that's%20sort%20of%20what%20drove%20me%20even%20more%20to%20choose%20this%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Antinori%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20Four%20Seasons%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20offered%20him%20a%20position%20in%202017%2C%20he%20jumped%20at%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Hong%20Kong%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20not%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20saw%20it%20from%20afar%2C%20it%20always%20looked%20extremely%20busy%2C%20and%20kind%20of%20trashy%2C%20like%20a%20big%20amusement%20park%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20moved%20here%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20city.%20I%20loved%20the%20contrast%20with%20having%20a%20very%20modern%2C%20busy%2C%20and%20high-paced%20city%2C%20but%20then%20you%20have%20so%20much%20nature%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Antinori%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20launched%20his%20own%20bar%2C%20Bar%20Leone%2C%20in%20Hong%20Kong's%20western%20Sheung%20Wan%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292a411e7-6c7f-41be-9bee-82152dac472e%5C%22%3EAn%20ode%20to%20his%20Italian%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20Antinori's%20bar%20is%20full%20of%20photographs%20and%20decor%20that%20harkens%20back%20to%20his%20Italian%20roots.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687dacc63d5881a51c1da8a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20Antinori's%20bar%20is%20full%20of%20photographs%20and%20decor%20that%20harkens%20back%20to%20his%20Italian%20roots.%3Cp%3EBar%20Leone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAntinori%20wanted%20Bar%20Leone%20to%20feel%20like%20an%20Italian%20caf%C3%A9.%20The%20bar's%20walls%20are%20decorated%20with%20pictures%20of%20Italian%20actors%20like%20Sabrina%20Ferilli%2C%20local%20football%20teams%2C%20and%20composer%20Ennio%20Morricone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20his%20drinks%20%26quot%3Bcocktail%20populari%2C%26quot%3B%20Italian%20for%20%26quot%3Bcocktail%20for%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20They're%20priced%20from%20120%20Hong%20Kong%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2415%2C%20to%20HK%24150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20of%20Antinori's%20bestsellers%20are%20the%20Olive%20Oil%20Sour%20and%20the%20Mortadella%20Focaccia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687dac34f748d8c055f5f08e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20of%20Antinori's%20bestsellers%20are%20the%20Olive%20Oil%20Sour%20and%20the%20Mortadella%20Focaccia.%3Cp%3EBar%20Leone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20most%20popular%20drinks%20is%20the%20%26quot%3BOlive%20Oil%20Sour%2C%26quot%3B%20made%20from%20whiskey%20sour%2C%20cherry%20whiskey%2C%20lemon%2C%20honey%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%20blended%20with%20egg%20white.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20drinks%2C%20Bar%20Leone%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20focaccia%20stuffed%20with%20cured%20pork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20serves%20200%20to%20300%20customers%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Antinori%2C%20a%20good%20bar%20is%20defined%20by%20good%20service%2C%20music%2C%20and%20quality.%20And%20his%20pet%20peeve%20is%20bad%20lighting%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20it's%20too%20bright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20have%20the%20same%20lighting%20and%20music%20from%205%20to%2011%20p.m.%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bar%20clinched%20second%20place%20on%20The%20World's%2050%20Best%20Restaurants'%20list%20of%20the%20best%2050%20bars%20in%202024%20and%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20publishing%20company's%20write-up%20this%20year%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20team%20are%20known%20for%20their%20warm%20hospitali