0and%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20districts%20impacted%20by%20mining%20activity.%20The%20parliamentarians%2C%20responding%20to%20feedback%20from%20local%20leaders%2C%20wanted%20to%20deploy%20these%20funds%20more%20efficiently%20and%20with%20greater%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20initial%20conversations%2C%20we%20started%20testing%20out%20the%20waters%20by%20walking%20through%20district%20administrations%20overseeing%20these%20DMFT%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20%3Cstrong%3ERwitwika%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Swaniti%20Initiative%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20champion%20bureaucrats%20at%20the%20time%20who%20really%20wanted%20to%20deploy%20their%20resources%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20communities%20they%20were%20serving.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swaniti%20began%20by%20working%20with%20local%20leaders%20and%20officials%20to%20align%20DMFT%20funds%20with%20community%20priorities.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477375%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESwaniti%20began%20by%20working%20with%20local%20leaders%20and%20officials%20to%20align%20DMFT%20funds%20with%20community%20priorities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20with%20pilot%20programmes%20in%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20districts%20led%20by%20progressive%20district%20magistrates%20%3Cstrong%3EB%20Rajeshwari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ERai%20Mahimapat%20Ray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(both%202011%20batch%20IAS%20officers).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20focussed%20on%20figuring%20out%20what%20their%20communities%20needed%20and%20finding%20more%20sustainable%20economic%20opportunities%20for%20them%20aligned%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20(SDGs).%20Soon%2C%20we%20deployed%20our%20fellows%20to%20start%20working%20out%20how%20DMFT%20resources%20could%20be%20aligned%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rwitwika%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20early%20efforts%20triggered%20a%20broader%20response.%20As%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20fellows%20embedded%20themselves%20within%20the%20local%20administrations%2C%20more%20district%20officials%20began%20to%20explore%20how%20DMFT%20funds%20could%20better%20serve%20%3Cstrong%3Evulnerable%20groups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20especially%20%3Cstrong%3Einformal%20mining%20workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Many%20administrators%20started%20mapping%20out%20economic%20alternatives%20and%20sought%20to%20unlock%20public%20funds%20to%20support%20these%20pathways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20role%20evolved.%20What%20began%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20optimise%20DMFT%20usage%20expanded%20to%20include%20convergence%20with%20other%20State%20and%20Union%20government%20schemes.%20The%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20%3Cstrong%3Eenabling%20a%20%E2%80%98just%20transition%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94ensuring%20that%20com