Rwitwika.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20philanthropic%20support%20came%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20Swaniti%E2%80%99s%20technical%20team%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20funding%20required%20to%20run%20these%20programmes%20for%20local%20communities%20came%20from%20government-sponsored%20schemes.%20Our%20task%20was%20to%20help%20them%20identify%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20community%2C%20map%20out%20where%20public%20funds%20are%20needed%20and%20mobilise%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EGaurav%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20with%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%2C%20recalls%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20their%20work%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20coal%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20we%20ended%20up%20having%20a%20presence%20across%20all%20mining%20districts%2C%20in%20the%20initial%20months%2C%20our%20team%20was%20actually%20working%20on%20unlocking%20those%20funds%2C%20which%20were%20present%20at%20the%20DMFT-level%20in%20Ramgarh%20and%20Bokaro%20districts.%20The%20DMFT%20fund%20is%20split%20between%20high-priority%20and%20non-priority%20areas.%20So%2C%20our%20team%20did%20a%20mapping%20exercise%20to%20identify%20high%20priority%20and%20low%20priority%20areas%20and%20where%20there%20is%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20underutilised%20funds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mapping%20DMFT%20funds%20revealed%20untapped%20resources%20that%20could%20be%20channelled%20to%20empower%20smallholder%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-3_11zon-1753712301.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2