roduce%20harvested%20by%20farmers%20in%20these%20FPOs%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20clause%20aimed%20to%20incentivise%20the%20adoption%20of%20solar%20drying%20technology%20and%20ensure%20early%20returns%20for%20farmers.%20Starting%20with%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20model%20soon%20expanded%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EDumka%2C%20Chaibasa%2C%20Latehar%2C%20and%20Chatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94the%20latter%20emerging%20as%20the%20most%20successful%20district%20in%20mobilising%20public%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20dryers%20with%20buyback%20guarantees%20helped%20farmers%20adopt%20technology%20and%20secure%20early%20profits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-4_11zon-1753712413-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%20with%20buyback%20guarantees%20helped%20farmers%20adopt%20technology%20and%20secure%20early%20profits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20core%20implementation%20of%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EJH-RESET%20project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20took%20place%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%20its%20foundation%20was%20laid%20as%20early%20as%202018%E2%80%9319.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20solar%20dryers%20alone%2C%20Swaniti%20reports%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Emonthly%20income%20increase%20of%20%E2%82%B93%2C000%E2%80%93%E2%82%B94%2C000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20mobilised%20about%20%E2%82%B955%20crore%20from%20three%20types%20of%20public%20funds%E2%80%94DMFT%2C%20SCF%20(State%20Co-operative%20Federation)%20and%20the%20Aspirational%20District%20Programme%20(ADP).%20This%20money%20was%20utilised%20to%20procure%20solar-powered%20cold%20storage%20and%20dryers.%20There%20was%20one%20cold%20storage%20facility%20distributed%20for%20three%20FPOs%2C%20and%20the%20solar%20dryers%20were%20allocated%20to%20each%20FPO.%20We%20had%20an%20active%20cohort%20of%20about%20200%20farmers%2C%20largely%20involved%20in%20growing%20tomatoes%2C%20given%20that%20it%20is%20the%20crop%20with%20the%20highest%20price%20slippage.%20With%20access%20to%20a%20dryer%20and%20cold%20storage%2C%20farmers%20saw%20the%20overall%20annual%20income%20of%20these%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20solar%20dryer%2C%20supplied%20by%20vendors%2C%20costs%20approximately%20%E2%82%B918%E2%80%93%E2%82%B919%20lakhs.%20Distribution%20took%20place%20in%20%3Cstrong%3Ethree%20phases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20starting%20with%20DMFT%20support%2C%20followed%20by%20funding%20from%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EDirectorate%20of%20Horticulture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EAspirational%20District%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%20Rs%2055%20crore%20was%20mobilised%20to%20install%20solar%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%2C%20boosting%20farmer%20incomes%20across%20Jharkhand.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753712646-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%20Rs%2055%20crore%20was%20mobilised%20to%20install%20solar%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%2C%20boosting%20farmer%20incomes%20across%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20almost%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20from%20the%20date%20of%20releasing%20the%20expression%20of%20interest%20to%20finding%20adequate%20vendors%2C%20to%20changing%20the%20RFP%20policy%20and%20then%20finally%20doing%20the%20demonstration.%20Although%20willingness%20and%20resources%20were%20often%20available%2C%20our%20program%20delivery%20designs%20tended%20to%20be%20overly%20complex%20and%20to%20cause%20delays%20in%20funding.%20The%20year%202020%E2%80%9321%20was%20spent%20on%20getting%20these%20dryers%20and%20cold%20storages%20out%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20months%20of%20demonstrations%20from%20private%20vendors%20to%20FPOs%2C%20showing%20farmers%20how%20to%20use%20this%20equipment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gaurav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20implementation%2C%20farmers%20were%20trained%20to%20use%20the%20new%20technology.%20%3Cstrong%3EAbdul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Latehar%2C%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%