eness%20and%20Mobilisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EMany%20companies%20are%20still%20unaware%20of%20the%20existence%20and%20utility%20of%20local%20employment%20exchanges.%20This%20indicates%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20better%20outreach%20and%20information%20dissemination.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutreach%20and%20Communication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEmployment%20exchanges%20must%20proactively%20engage%20with%20employers%20across%20India%2C%20not%20just%20within%20Jharkhand%2C%20to%20broaden%20recruitment%20networks.%20Strategic%20collaborations%E2%80%94with%20local%20organisations%2C%20call%20centres%2C%20and%20CSR-backed%20training%20programs%20can%20generate%20new%20local%20employment%20avenues.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkill%20Training%20and%20Upskilling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EPublic-private%20partnerships%20with%20training%20providers%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20NSDC%20model%2C%20can%20strengthen%20skill%20development%20initiatives.%20The%20Career%20Centre%20should%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Skill%20Development%20Department%20to%20connect%20job%20seekers%20with%20online%20certification%2C%20government%20schemes%2C%20and%20sector-specific%20training.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInterdepartmental%20Coordination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEmployment%20exchanges%20can%20act%20as%20intermediaries%20to%20help%20employers%20navigate%20permits%2C%20licenses%2C%20and%20access%20to%20subsidies%20by%20coordinating%20across%20government%20departments%E2%80%94making%20the%20process%20less%20fragmented.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDatabase%20of%20Informal%20Workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%3Cbr%3EEstablishing%20a%20digital%20registry%20of%20informal%20workers%2C%20especially%20in%20sectors%20like%20waste%20management%2C%20is%20essential%20for%20transitioning%20them%20into%20formal%2C%20stable%20employment.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%