phew%20Tridip%20Patir%3B%20his%20bonds%20with%20them%20were%20instinctive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201903%2C%20Mahi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epenchant%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%20in%20his%20home%20village%2C%20Alimur%2C%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Lakhimpur.%20His%20discipline%20came%20from%20his%20father%2C%20Doley%20Miri%2C%20a%20man%20respected%20by%20the%20community.%20His%20beginnings%20were%20humble%3B%20Mahi%20and%20his%20brother%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20makeshift%20thatched%20cottage%20on%20a%20plot%20of%20hired%20land%20at%20Sivasagar.%20The%20boys%20attended%20the%20Sivasagar%20Town%20Government%20HE%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tennis%20aficionado%2C%20Mahi%20often%20played%20legendary%20sportsman%20Prof%20PC%20Roy.%20He%20was%20hardworking%3B%20%E2%80%9Csoft-spoken%20and%20disciplined%E2%80%9D%20is%20how%20most%20described%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahi%20was%20known%20for%20wearing%20his%20passion%20on%20his%20sleeve%2C%20at%20least%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20those%20who%20knew%20him%20well%20recall.%20Tridip%2C%20while%20looking%20to%20pursue%20his%20doctoral%20thesis%20in%20human-nature%20relationships%2C%20took%20a%20trip%20down%20memory%20lane%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20an%20understanding%20of%20the%20topic%20was%20impossible%20without%20learning%20more%20about%20his%20exemplar%20great-uncle.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20many%20in%20Assam%20are%20familiar%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20celebrated%20Padma%20Shri%20educationist%20Indira%20Miri%2C%20few%20know%20about%20Mahi%20Chandra%20Miri%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unfortunate%20because%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467900%2Findian-wildlife-conservation-heroes-turtles-tigers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtributions%20to%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20role%20in%20establishing%20Kaziranga%E2%80%99s%20protected%20status%20were%20immense.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20transforming%20Kaziranga%20from%20a%20neglected%20wilderness%20into%20a%20world-renowned%20conservation%20landmark%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tridip%20remarks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaziranga%20has%20had%20quite%20a%20chequered%20journey.%20It%20was%20Mary%20Curzon%2C%20Lord%20Curzon%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20whose%20interventions%20helped%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20reserve%20forest%20in%201905%2C%20when%20she%20failed%20to%20see%20any%20rhinoceros%20on%20her%20trip%20to%20the%20park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hoof%20marks%20in%20the%20forest%20did%20nothing%20to%20improve%20her%20mood.%20It%20was%20Balaram%20Hazarika%2C%20an%20eponymous%20animal%20tracker%20from%20Assam%2C%20who%20emphasised%20the%20urgent%20requirement%20for%20wildlife%20conservation%20to%20Mrs%20Curzon%2C%20who%20asked%20her%20husband%20to%20do%20something.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%201%20June%201905%20Kaziranga%20Proposed%20Reserve%20Forest%20was%20created.%20But%20by%201938%2C%20its%20existence%20was%20threatened%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F469442%2Fprofessor-rajib-tariang-empowers-assam-hunting-community-to-become-protectors-of-wildlife-promotes-eco-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erampant%20hunting%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20a%20shadow%20of%20its%20current%20self.%20Tridip%20credits%20his%20great-uncle%20for%20the%20real%20on-ground%20transformation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inflection%20point%20in%20Mahi%E2%80%99s%20life%20came%20in%201929%2C%20when%20he%2C%20along%20with%20officer%20Madhab%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20was%20selected%20for%20the%20Imperial%20Forest%20Service.%20The%20duo%20was%20sent%20to