uploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568-500x509.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cawasji%20Patel%20mango%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568-500x509.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568-295x300.jpg%20295w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568-150x153.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FCourtesy-Springers-The-Mango-Genome_11zon-1753443568.jpg%20629w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20considered%20obscure%20and%20rare%20in%20Indian%20markets.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECawasji%20Patel%20funded%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20water%20tank%20to%20address%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20drinking%20water%20shortages%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20area%20being%20named%20after%20him.%20The%20tank%2C%20now%20defunct%2C%20is%20historically%20important%20as%20part%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20early%20water%20infrastructure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20is%20tied%20to%20public%20infrastructure%20philanthropy.%20The%20Gazetteer%20of%20Bombay%20City%20and%20Island%20(1909)%20notes%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20the%20water%20project.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%2C%20as%20Bombay%20grew%2C%20a%20mango%20was%20named%20after%20him%E2%80%94a%20tribute%20from%20a%20city%20that%20remembered%20its%20patrons%20in%20sweet%2C%20lasting%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrown%20in%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20orchards%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20of%20Powai%20Lake%2C%20it%20later%20spread%20to%20orchards%20springing%20up%20in%20Thane%20and%20Pune.%20The%20Powai%20estate%20had%20one%20lakh%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fidiya.net%2Fp%2Fkavasji-patel-framji-kavasji-banaji-mumbais-forgotten-heros%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20mango%20trees%20spread%20over%201334%20acres%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F402943%2Findia-mango-map-hidden-guide-season%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emango%20growing%20here%20was%20popular%20%3C%2Fa%3Eamong%20the%20British%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CBombay%20Mango%E2%80%9D.%20In%201833-34%2C%20it%20was%20more%20expensive%20than%20Ratnagiri%E2%80%99s%20mango.%20On%20May%2018%2C%201838%2C%20a%20basket%20of%20this%20famous%20Bombay%20Mango%20was%20sent%20to%20Queen%20Victoria%20of%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreen%20fruit%20with%20white%20pulp%3A%20What%20made%20this%20mago%20unique%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fruit%20was%20typically%20harvested%20green%20with%20white%20pulp%2C%20making%20it%20unique%20among%20mangoes.%20It%20was%20fibreless%2C%20which%20made%20it%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20cooking%2C%20especially%20for%20making%20jams%20and%20jellies%E2%80%94a%20quality%20appreciated%20by%20both%20Europeans%20and%20the%20Parsee%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20in%20Vechale%2C%20Cawasji%20Patel%20lives%20again%E2%80%94not%20in%20stone%20or%20brass%2C%20but%20in%20the%20flesh%20of%20a%20mango%2C%20sweet%20with%20memory%20and%20dripping%20with%20reverence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FA-Close-up-view-of-mango-tree-at-Deshmukh-familys-farm_11zon-1753443530.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cawasji%20Patel%20mango%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%