ng%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20thousands%20of%20fisherfolk%20who%20depended%20on%20the%20wetland%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20A%20joint%20mission%3A%20Government%20and%20communities%20unite%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restoration%20of%20Muthupet%E2%80%99s%20mangroves%20was%20launched%20under%20the%20%3Cstrong%3EGreen%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Mission%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20between%20%3Cstrong%3E2022%20and%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20led%20by%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiruvarur%20Forest%20Division%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20under%20%3Cstrong%3EDistrict%20Forest%20Officer%20(DFO)%20LCS%20Srikanth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EState-wide%20oversight%20by%20%3Cstrong%3ESupriya%20Sahu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20Environment%2C%20Forests%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Department%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20made%20this%20mission%20unique%20was%20the%20%3Cstrong%3Eintegration%20of%20scientific%20planning%20with%20grassroots%20participation%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20Officials%20mobilised%20over%20%3Cstrong%3E10%2C000%20residents%20from%2016%20fishing%20villages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20including%20Veerankoil%20and%20Thondiyakadu%2C%20through%20the%20formation%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EVillage%20Mangrove%20Councils%20(VMCs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20These%20councils%20became%20%3Cstrong%3Elocal%20governance%20units%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20combining%20traditional%20knowledge%20with%20structured%20ecological%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20members%20contributed%20to%20everything%20from%20planting%20and%20guarding%20saplings%20to%20repairing%20canals%20and%20ensuring%20regular%20tidal%20flow.%20This%20sense%20of%20%3Cstrong%3Eshared%20ownership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20was%20central%20to%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20viability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYou%20are%20looking%20at%20the%20incredible%20Fishbone%20canals%20of%20Muthupet%20in%20Thiruvarur%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20created%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20This%20is%20a%20scientifically%20proven%20method%20for%20mangrove%20plantation%20adopted%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department.%20The%20canal%20design%20features%20a%20deep%20main%20feeder%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FE9KOag0IZt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FE9KOag0IZt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Supriya%20Sahu%20IAS%20(%40supriyasahuias)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsupriyasahuias%2Fstatus%2F1938806165229707581%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2028%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20How%20they%20did%20it%3A%20Scientific%20design%20meets%20traditional%20knowledge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA.%20Canal%20network%20design%3A%20Enabling%20natural%20tidal%20flushing%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20challenges%20was%20%3Cstrong%3Erestoring%20natural%20tidal%20flow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20waterlogged%20or%20dry%20zones.%20This%20was%20addressed%20through%20two%20engineering%20models%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFishbone%20Design%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mimicking%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20fish%20skeleton%2C%20this%20model%20creates%20a%20central%20canal%20with%20smaller%20lateral%20canals%20extending%20outward.%20It%20allows%20tidal%20waters%20to%20%3Cstrong%3Eflow%20deep%20into%20mangrove%20areas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20enabling%20proper%20flushing%2C%20salinity%20balance%2C%20and%20seed%20dispersal.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBox%20Des